[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Brands Hatch Grand Prix[/b]
Week 12 of 12 - 2018 Season 4 [/size][/color]
Race Distance: [b]18 laps[/b], approximately 25 minutes
World Record lap time: [b]1:39.623[/b] by Mike Galloway (qualifying)
(n.b. random/dynamic weather impacts lap times greatly)

For week 12 we're off to England's famous Brands Hatch track at the Grand Prix layout. With it's stunning scenery and undulating track it makes for spectacular racing. For the newbies - check out the lap guides, you can easily gain seconds per lap knowing which corners you can/should cut.

Target "planned" SoF race is usually 20:45 GMT Sunday, immediately following the Weekend Warriors league race.

